        <abstract id="ABS3" abstract-type="summary">
          <title>In Brief</title>
          <p id="P7">Integrating longitudinal transcriptomic and genomic data from paired diffuse glioma samples with complementary single-cell RNAseq and multiplex immunofluorescence datasets reveals recurrence-associated genetic and microenvironmental changes that are dependent on IDH mutation status.</p>
